{
  "texts": [
    "Next, based on the ideal values of the variables employed in the optimization, the optimal cost is calculated.",
    "In this optimization technique, the input populations of the grasshoppers are updated for the prediction of best optimum value.",
    "Since the updating populations can be repeated in this case, the location can always be altered.",
    "Thus, in order to complete the feature selection process, it is helpful to obtain both the local and global optimal values.",
    "Just the local optimal value has been determined in relation to the weight function in the traditional grasshopper model."
  ]
}